body.description: "Unitizing the latest USB 3.2 Gen 2x2 technology, this portable SSD boost transfer speed of up to 2000MB/s, offering you amazing performance to transfer and store high-res photos, vides, movies, content creations, and more. Universally compatible with various operating systems like Windows, Mac, Android, and Linux, this Type-C external SSD coming with a USB C to USB A cable and a USB C to USB C cable supports all your USB-C and USB-A devices, such as PCs, laptops, tablets, smartphones, game consoles, etc. Designed in mini size of 93.4x51.5x11mm/3.7x2x0.4inch and weighing only 57g/2oz, this slim portable solid state drive with protective silicone case, letting you fit into your pocket or purse to travel with you anywhere. Shockproof, waterproof, drop-proof, this USB-C external SSD would be your perfect companion for use on the go. Note: 1GB = 1,000,000,000 bytes, 1TB = 1,000,000,000,000 bytes. Actual use capacity less. The speed may be different depending on host devices, interface, and usage conditions.
